# VS Code extension: "REST Client" (Huachao Mao)
# Usage: open this file, then click "Send Request" above each request.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### Health check (example)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hello

### Upload photo (multipart/form-data)
# OpenAPI: POST /photos, requestBody: multipart/form-data, field: file (binary)
# Token is optional. If you want to send it, add:
#   X-Github-Token: <token>
POST {{baseUrl}}/photos
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./tools/restclient/sample.jpg
--boundary--
